docs {
  # Update User Profile
  
  Updates the current user's profile information (name and/or email).
  
  **Authentication:** Required (JWT cookie)
  
  **Request Body:**
  ```json
  {
    "name": "John Smith",
    "email": "john@example.com"
  }
  ```
  
  **Response:**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Profile updated successfully",
    "data": {
      "id": 1,
      "email": "john@example.com",
      "name": "John Smith",
      "is_active": true,
      "created_at": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2024-01-02T00:00:00.000Z"
    }
  }
  ```
}
